        "date": "2025-07-23T14:05:00Z",
        "message": "Improve sign interaction check\n\nThis adds an additional access check on the SignChangeEvent to\n prevent plugins from uncancelling the interaction on right click\n on a sign to prevent editing of the sign being possible with in\n some setups even though ChestShop did not allow it.\n\nAlso improve how the access ignoring and sign dying is handled on\n interaction in general as well as allow admins to edit Admin Shops.",
